{
  "name": "Drive \u2192 Shopify Image Sync",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Drive \u2192 Shopify Image Sync\n\n**Two-phase architecture (no nested loops):**\n\n**Phase 1 \u2014 Collect** (Iterate Sheets loop)\n`Load Sheet Names \u2192 Iterate Sheets \u2192 Read Sheet Rows \u2192 Collect to Static Data`\nReads all 19 sheets one at a time using the dedicated Google Sheets node.\nFiltered product rows are accumulated in workflow static data.\n\n**Phase 2 \u2014 Process** (Iterate Products loop)\n`Get Collected Products \u2192 Iterate Products \u2192 Drive lookups \u2192 Upload \u2192 Update Sheet`\nStarts only after Phase 1 finishes. Processes the flat list of products one at a time.\n\n**Image naming (case-insensitive before extension):**\n- Filename ending `-P` \u2192 IMAGE URL1 + Picture column\n- Filename ending `-S` \u2192 IMAGE URL2\n- All others \u2192 IMAGE URL3, IMAGE URL4 \u2026\n\n**Setup:** Connect Google Drive OAuth2 and Shopify OAuth2 credentials.\nGoogle Sheets (`Template_control`) is already wired.",
        "height": 480,
        "width": 620
      },
      "id": "87002b6c-55ee-47e4-948d-57694d828c19",
      "name": "README",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        74448,
        12864
      ]
    },
